                    <li><a class="dropdown-item text-orange" href="/posts/algorithms/graph">Graph Algorithms</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item text-orange" href="/posts/algorithms/dynamic-programming">Dynamic
                            Programming</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item text-orange" href="/posts/algorithms/recursion">Recursion</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item text-orange" href="/posts/algorithms/greedy">Greedy Algorithms</a></li>
